SplashNext !ARMovie

| Add newer codecs to ResourceFS
AddToRes STBResources:!ARMovie Apps.!ARMovie

| Ensure we have the modules we need to treat volume correctly
RMCheck SoundFX       0.22 SoundFX
RMCheck FilePlay      0.04 FilePlay
RMCheck ReplaySupport 0.41 ReplaySpt

| A volume of -30 corresponds to -11.3 dB
SoundFXVolume -30
